title: Pumpkin Swirl Bowl
description:
At the end of a blow pipe, orange, burgundy, gold colored glass is meticulously layered then manipulated to create intricate patterns and movement. The pumpkin is finished with a gold luster vine and adorned with a leaf.  Handmade in the USA.  Each piece is unique.  Slight variations may occur.

6 1/2 x 6 1/4 in. with a 3 x 3 1/2 in. opening.
